	 <scopecontent> 
		<p>Oral history interview, biographical features, correspondence,
		  financial records, writings, newsletters, clippings, ephemera, manuscripts.
		  Most of the material concerns the Everett Massacre and Industrial Workers of
		  the World.</p> 
	 </scopecontent> 
